Allure reports Generation

1. Install Package Allure-behave by command
    pip install allure-behave

2. Run command for report generation
    behave -f allure_behave.formatter:AllureFormatter -o "<Specify folder name>" featurefilefolder/

3. If you face hurdles in generating allure reports for first time
    Follow below steps
    Step1: Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser
    Step2: irm get.scoop.sh | iex
    Step3: scoop install allure
